## Open Source Libraries

**c2c-common** — CGI SE Trusted Services
- Java implementation of IEEE 1609.2 (US) and ETSI TS 103 097 / 102 941 (EU) V2X PKI data structures and generators.
- Used as the core cryptographic library dependency in Cert-V2X.
- License: AGPL-3.0
- https://github.com/CGI-SE-Trusted-Services/c2c-common

**Bouncy Castle**
- JCE provider for ECDSA P-256 and Brainpool P-256r1 cryptographic operations, required by c2c-common.
- License: MIT
- https://www.bouncycastle.org/

**Spring Boot 3**
- REST API framework for the Cert-V2X service layer.
- License: Apache 2.0
- https://spring.io/projects/spring-boot

